com.appglu.android.sync
Class SyncBroadcastReceiver

java.lang.Object
  android.content.BroadcastReceiver
      com.appglu.android.sync.SyncBroadcastReceiver

public abstract class SyncBroadcastReceiver
extends android.content.BroadcastReceiver

Create a sub-class of SyncBroadcastReceiver to receive broadcast events from SyncIntentService.

To register this BroadcastReceiver use a SyncIntentFilter like below:

Activity.this.registerReceiver(syncBroadcastReceiver, new SyncIntentFilter());

Since:
1.0.0
See Also:
SyncIntentFilter
